18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1-201 of Title 70, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 A. Subject to the availability of funds, Seven Million Five
22 Hundred Thousand Dollars ($7,500,000.00) shall be allocated by the
23 State Board of Education to provide grants to public middle schools,
